<p><a name="Life_and_work" id="Life_and_work"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=K._Eric_Drexler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Life and work">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Life and work</span></h2>
<table class="infobox" style="text-align:center; font-size:95%;">
<tr>
<td style="background:#eaa986; padding:0.25em 0.75em; width:16em;">
<p><small>Part of a series of articles on</small><br />
<b><span style="font-size:170%;"><a href="/wiki/Molecular_nanotechnology" title="Molecular nanotechnology">Molecular<br />
Nanotechnology</a></span></b></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background:#eaa986;"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background:#f4d5b7;">
<p><a href="/wiki/Molecular_assembler" title="Molecular assembler">Molecular assembler</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Mechanosynthesis" title="Mechanosynthesis">Mechanosynthesis</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Molecular_machine" title="Molecular machine">Molecular machine</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Productive_nanosystems" title="Productive nanosystems">Productive nanosystems</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Nanorobotics" title="Nanorobotics">Nanorobotics</a><br />
<strong class="selflink">K. Eric Drexler</strong><br />
<i><a href="/wiki/Engines_of_Creation" title="Engines of Creation">Engines of Creation</a></i><br />
<a href="/wiki/Grey_goo" title="Grey goo">Grey goo</a></p>
</td>
